@node was


  ShisenSho is a Chinese mindgame. It will played with the same Stones
  as Mahjong, but with total other rules.

  To make the game interesting, I add some new rules.

    1.) Multiplier-Stones
        -----------------
        The Points would calculate with the Multiplier-Stones.
        With some Stones, this multipier can raise.

    2.) More Points by longer ways.
        ---------------------------
        Ever longer a way between a pair, all so much the points.
        This way is in related with the multipier.

  So you can influence the points, through clever solution.

    3.) Help
        ----
        You can, if you have helps left, blast Stones away.
        So it is much easyier, to solve a Level.
        But it is much profitable, to use no helps.

@endnode was


